data.description: Discover the allure of this beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom all-brick home, boasting over 1,400 sqft of comfortable living space. Nestled conveniently near schools, shopping, dining, beaches, and Tyndall Air Force Base, this residence offers a blend of convenience and charm. The roof was replaced in 2019, and the interior features tile floors, updated light fixtures, and a spacious kitchen adorned with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a breakfast bar. Relax on the covered back porch overlooking a generous backyard with a storage building. The master bedroom offers ample space, and its updated bathroom showcases a tiled shower, granite countertops, and modern fixtures. Two additional rooms provide plenty of accommodation for family and guests, with an updated guest bathroom featuring a new vanity and tiled shower. This home combines modern amenities with a touch of elegance, featuring a formal dining room and a full-size laundry room for added convenience. Don't miss the chance to make this property your new home - schedule a viewing today!
